"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 795, \"end\": 804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.7033017038986968, \"rank\": 0.3422081883331307, \"text\": \"Spaniards\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a second Olympic medal for the family of South African-born van der Westhuyzen, after his older brother Jean won gold in Tokyo in the K2, which he will line up in again in Paris.\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 986, \"end\": 991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999018911038923, \"rank\": 9.727645425845238e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999245119, \"rank\": 7.537972185243202e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ABC Sportis live blogging every day of the Paris Olympics  ABC Sportis live blogging every day of the Paris Olympics  The Australian men's Olympic campaign started slowly, finishing a shock third in their heat on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1045, \"end\": 1048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999954473813836, \"rank\": 4.552638841134832e-06, \"text\": \"ABC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 1104, \"end\": 1107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999954473813836, \"rank\": 4.552638841134832e-06, \"text\": \"ABC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 1163, \"end\": 1177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.344897041568133e-21, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in the semifinal, raced earlier Thursday, they made a statement by setting a new Olympic best time in the event.\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That time, 1:19.22, would have won them gold in the final.\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We left it out there, all the way to the line.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Can not be upset with what we put down there,\\\" Havard told the Nine Network.\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.723591382219758e-15, \"text\": \"Nine Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The teams had to wait for official confirmation of the winner, such was the narrow margin between gold and silver.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Want more?Here's the full list of all our Olympics stories  Not letting the margin of defeat dampen his spirits, Fitzsimmons said after the race he hoped the crew would encourage juniors in the same way he was inspired by the Australian team in London 2012.\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1914, \"end\": 1929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.7514178059398023, \"rank\": 0.33059956692589354, \"text\": \"Australian team\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1933, \"end\": 1944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.633752063579145e-15, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the motto for that Olympics was 'Inspire a generation'.\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 2011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They certainly inspired us.\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope we inspired a few people back at home today,\\\" he told the Nine Network.\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2105, \"end\": 2117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.723591382219758e-15, \"text\": \"Nine Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the Australian women's K4 crew of Ella Beere, Aly Bull, Alexandra Clarke and Yale Steinepreis were last in their final, won by New Zealand with veteran Lisa Carrington winning her sixth gold among an Olympic haul of nine medals.\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2135,